in the phrase “appropriate comment and recommendations” is omitted as unnecessary. The words “to the head of the agency concerned” are added for clarity.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (e), the substance of the definition of “physician” in former section 790 is substituted for the reference to that section.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (f)(2) and (3), the words “Canal Zone Government” and “Panama Canal Company” are substituted for “Panama Canal” and “Panama Railroad”, respectively, on the authority of the ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1950-09-26/ch1049/s2/a"},"text":"Act of Sept. 26, 1950, ch. 1049, § 2(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/64/1038"},"text":"64 Stat. 1038","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The last proviso of the first sentence of the Act of ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1946-08-08"},"text":"Aug. 8, 1946","children":[],"tail":", is omitted as executed."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Standard changes are made to conform with the definitions applicable and the style of this title as outlined in the preface to the report.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"historicalAndRevision","id":"idb8b94790-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"1967 ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Act","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This section amends ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t5/s7901"},"text":"5 U.S.C. 7901","children":[],"tail":" to reflect 1966 Reorganization Plan No. 3, effective "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1966-06-25"},"text":"June 25, 1966","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/80/1610"},"text":"80 Stat. 1610","children":[],"tail":", section 1 of which transferred all functions of the Public Health Service to the Secretary of Health, Education, and Welfare."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idb8b94791-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idb8b94792-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1996—Subsec. (f). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/201"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–201","children":[],"tail":" amended subsec. (f) generally. Prior to amendment, subsec. (f) read as follows: “The health programs conducted by the following agencies are not affected by this section—"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(1) the Tennessee Valley Authority;","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(2) the Canal Zone Government; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(3) the Panama Canal Company.”","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idb8b94793-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"changeOfName","id":"idb8b94794-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Change of Name","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Secretary of Health, Education, and Welfare redesignated Secretary of Health and Human Services by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s3508"},"text":"section 3508 of Title 20","children":[],"tail":", Education."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"shortTitleOfAmendment","id":"idb8b94795-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Short Title of 1993 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/172/s1/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–172, § 1(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-12-02"},"text":"Dec. 2, 1993","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/107/1995"},"text":"107 Stat. 1995","children":[],"tail":", provided that: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/103/172/s1/a"},"text":"“This Act [enacting ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t5/s7905"},"text":"section 7905 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and provisions set out as notes under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t5/s7905"},"text":"section 7905 of this title","children":[],"tail":"] may be cited as the ‘Federal Employees Clean Air Incentives Act’.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"idb8b94796-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Demonstration Project: Health Protection; Health Promotion; Disease Prevention; and Secondary Prevention","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/251/tI/s110"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–251, title I, § 110","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-02-27"},"text":"Feb. 27, 1986","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/100/17"},"text":"100 Stat. 17","children":[],"tail":", directed Director of Office of Personnel Management to conduct a demonstration project to determine most effective method of furnishing health protection, health promotion, disease prevention, and secondary prevention services to Federal Government employees, with Director to report to Congress no later than 60 days after termination of project on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-02-27"},"text":"Feb. 27, 1988","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
